com.team6.project.readers

Class Reader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team6.project.readers.Reader
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseDataReader, EventCauseReader, FailureTypeReader, OperatorCountryReader, UserEquipmentReader

    public abstract class Reader
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class Reader defines the generic behavior of each specific reader. It implements basic methods used to retrieve a specific Type from an excel cell (Numeric Cell, String Cell, Date Cell)
    Author:
    Cristiana
